# ForgeKit Lite - Cursor Rules

## Project Overview

**ForgeKit Lite** — A production monorepo starter (React 19 + Hono + Turborepo) with an AI workflow layer for structured, phase-based development.

## Monorepo Structure

```
forgekit-lite/
├── apps/
│   ├── web/                    # React 19 + Vite + Tailwind 4
│   └── api/                    # Hono API server
├── packages/
│   ├── shared/                 # Types, constants, utilities
│   └── ui/                     # UI component library
└── docs/                       # Documentation
    ├── PRODUCTION_ROADMAP.md   # Phase overview (generated by /kickstart)
    └── phases/                 # Phase-based task planning
```

## Key Documents

- `CURRENT_FOCUS.md` — Active work context
- `docs/PRODUCTION_ROADMAP.md` — Phase overview and progress
- `docs/COMMANDS.md` — AI commands reference

## Tech Stack

**Frontend:** React 19, TypeScript, Vite 6, Tailwind CSS 4
**Backend:** Node.js 22+, Hono 4
**Infrastructure:** pnpm workspaces, Turborepo

## Commands

```bash
pnpm dev              # Run all packages
pnpm build            # Build all
pnpm lint             # Linting
pnpm typecheck        # Type checking
pnpm test             # Run tests
```

## Available Commands

- `kickstart` — Initialize project documentation
- `start-session` — Load project context
- `plan-phase` — Generate phase task breakdown
- `check-task` — Mark tasks as complete
- `update-focus` — Update current work status
